translate spanish ep016_prison_b4be29a9:

#   woman "Understood."
    woman "Entendido."

# game/episode016.rpy:267
translate spanish ep016_prison_089bacd5:

#   "The woman stopped before one of the identical cells."
    "La mujer se detuvo ante una de las celdas idénticas."

# game/episode016.rpy:269
translate spanish ep016_prison_5a6e10eb:

#   woman "This unit houses the leader of the infiltration unit."
    woman "Esta unidad alberga al líder de la unidad de infiltración."

# game/episode016.rpy:270
translate spanish ep016_prison_16e69548:

#   woman "Only one other person is allowed inside the cell at all times."
    woman "Sólo se permite otra persona dentro de la celda en todo momento."

# game/episode016.rpy:271
translate spanish ep016_prison_83c045ba:

#   c "So I’ll be alone with the prisoner?"
    c "¿Así que estaré solo con el prisionero?"

# game/episode016.rpy:272
translate spanish ep016_prison_4d42fa27:

#   woman "Yes, you will."
    woman "Sí, lo harás."

# game/episode016.rpy:273
translate spanish ep016_prison_642aae34:

#   c "There’s video surveillance in the cell at least?"
    c "¿Hay videovigilancia en la celda al menos?"

# game/episode016.rpy:274
translate spanish ep016_prison_3c7134db:

#   woman "No, that’s not necessary."
    woman "No, no es necesario."

# game/episode016.rpy:275
translate spanish ep016_prison_8406d765:

#   woman "We allow our prisoners a certain privacy."
    woman "Permitimos a nuestros prisioneros cierta privacidad."

# game/episode016.rpy:276
translate spanish ep016_prison_4581f139:

#   ki "How do you ensure they don’t harm themselves?"
    ki "¿Cómo asegurarse de que no se hagan daño?"

# game/episode016.rpy:278
translate spanish ep016_prison_a1663295:

#   woman "Each prisoner has a chip embedded inside them."
    woman "Cada prisionero tiene un chip incrustado en su interior."

# game/episode016.rpy:279
translate spanish ep016_prison_0e76cf01:

#   woman "We closely monitor vitals and emotional disturbances."
    woman "Controlamos de cerca las constantes vitales y las alteraciones emocionales."

# game/episode016.rpy:280
translate spanish ep016_prison_685f6c4d:

#   na "And that’s enough?"
    na "¿Y eso es suficiente?"

# game/episode016.rpy:281
translate spanish ep016_prison_6a9c1a52:

#   woman "Yes, we only intervene when necessary."
    woman "Sí, sólo intervenimos cuando es necesario."

# game/episode016.rpy:282
translate spanish ep016_prison_df13be76:

#   woman "So far we have a mortality rate of zero."
    woman "Hasta ahora tenemos una tasa de mortalidad de cero."

# game/episode016.rpy:283
translate spanish ep016_prison_42be5669:

#   c "Impressive system in that case."
    c "Impresionante sistema en ese caso."

# game/episode016.rpy:285
translate spanish ep016_prison_67c1ad44:

#   woman "We like to think so."
    woman "Nos gusta pensar que sí."

# game/episode016.rpy:286
translate spanish ep016_prison_8ebf4249:

#   woman "Are you ready?"
    woman "¿Estás preparado?"

# game/episode016.rpy:287
translate spanish ep016_prison_b63d6bf3:

#   c "I am."
    c "Lo soy."

# game/episode016.rpy:289
translate spanish ep016_prison_97a74530:

#   woman "Very well, stand aside."
    woman "Muy bien, apártate."

# game/episode016.rpy:291
translate spanish ep016_prison_f2835e57:

#   "The guard opened the dimly lit cell which seemed completely empty."
    "El guardia abrió la celda poco iluminada, que parecía completamente vacía."

# game/episode016.rpy:293
translate spanish ep016_prison_100bc55f:

#   woman "Step inside please."
    woman "Entra, por favor."

# game/episode016.rpy:294
translate spanish ep016_prison_cd883530:

#   woman "This is just an antechamber, once I close the outer door, the inner door will open."
    woman "Esto es sólo una antesala, una vez que cierre la puerta exterior, la puerta interior se abrirá."

# game/episode016.rpy:296
translate spanish ep016_prison_cc68a8cf:

#   "I entered the cell and waited for the door to close."
    "Entré en la celda y esperé a que se cerrara la puerta."

# game/episode016.rpy:298
translate spanish ep016_prison_cef3aa88:

#   "The cell door closed with a hiss and the inner door slid open to reveal the prisoner."
    "La puerta de la celda se cerró con un silbido y la puerta interior se deslizó para dejar al descubierto al prisionero."

# game/episode016.rpy:299
translate spanish ep016_prison_d45eb29c:

#   "I wasn’t quite prepared for what I saw."
    "No estaba preparado para lo que vi."

# game/episode016.rpy:300
translate spanish ep016_prison_cab5397a:

#   "A snakelike form stood in front of me, parts of it glowing in the scarce light of the prison cell."
    "Delante de mí había una forma parecida a una serpiente, algunas de cuyas partes brillaban bajo la escasa luz de la celda."

# game/episode016.rpy:302
translate spanish ep016_prison_fec0d5b9:

#   "The alien looked vaguely human and had pronounced breasts and soft facial curves."
    "El alienígena parecía vagamente humano y tenía unos pechos pronunciados y suaves curvas faciales."

# game/episode016.rpy:303
translate spanish ep016_prison_c8f1393f:

#   "I wasn’t sure if the Scolguin even had a concept of sex or gender."
    "No estaba seguro de que los escolguines tuvieran siquiera un concepto de sexo o género."

# game/episode016.rpy:304
translate spanish ep016_prison_801c367a:

#   "Glowing strands sprouted from the creature’s head giving the impression of a hairpiece."
    "De la cabeza de la criatura brotaban hebras brillantes que daban la impresión de un postizo."

# game/episode016.rpy:306
translate spanish ep016_prison_51099d1c:

#   "The Scolguin rose and fixed its eyes upon me."
    "El escolguín se levantó y fijó sus ojos en mí."

# game/episode016.rpy:308
translate spanish ep016_prison_0c397c14:

#   xa "A visitor."
    xa "Un visitante."

# game/episode016.rpy:309
translate spanish ep016_prison_26eefe0a:

#   c "Yes."
    c "Sí."

# game/episode016.rpy:310
translate spanish ep016_prison_4c1981ca:

#   c "Do you have a name?"
    c "¿Tienes nombre?"

# game/episode016.rpy:312
translate spanish ep016_prison_df4f29e8:

#   xa "You may call me Xatrape."
    xa "Puedes llamarme Xatrape."

# game/episode016.rpy:314
translate spanish ep016_prison_e745f0d2:

#   c "You were part of the Scolguin incursion of Uailea."
    c "Usted fue parte de la incursión Scolguin de Uailea."

# game/episode016.rpy:316
translate spanish ep016_prison_7ebf8653:

#   xa "Don’t you have a name?"
    xa "¿No tienes nombre?"

# game/episode016.rpy:317
translate spanish ep016_prison_24e9fdab:

#   c "Please answer the question."
    c "Por favor, responda a la pregunta."

# game/episode016.rpy:319
translate spanish ep016_prison_568c8cfd:

#   xa "Why ask me something you already know."
    xa "Por qué preguntarme algo que ya sabes."

# game/episode016.rpy:320
translate spanish ep016_prison_0781896e:

#   xa "I’d rather know your name first."
    xa "Preferiría saber tu nombre primero."

# game/episode016.rpy:322
translate spanish ep016_prison_45b0c1e8:

#   xa "It breeds...{w} Trust..."
    xa "Genera...{w} Confianza..."

# game/episode016.rpy:323
translate spanish ep016_prison_385547f6:

#   xa "The Rhenkoy have withheld me from meeting new people for so long."
    xa "Los Rhenkoy me han impedido conocer gente nueva durante mucho tiempo."

# game/episode016.rpy:325
translate spanish ep016_prison_201eeb98:

#   xa "So very long..."
    xa "Tanto tiempo..."

# game/episode016.rpy:326
translate spanish ep016_prison_be17ee9b:

#   c "Answer the question."
    c "Responde a la pregunta."

# game/episode016.rpy:328
translate spanish ep016_prison_c2dbf3cd:

#   xa "I used to like meeting new people."
    xa "Me gustaba conocer gente nueva."

# game/episode016.rpy:329
translate spanish ep016_prison_eaa27b04:

#   xa "Tasting them for the first time."
    xa "Probarlos por primera vez."

# game/episode016.rpy:330
translate spanish ep016_prison_f6353130:

#   c "Tasting?"
    c "¿Degustación?"

# game/episode016.rpy:332
translate spanish ep016_prison_90f874bb:

#   xa "A figure of speech, I’m not sure if there’s a good translation in your language."
    xa "Una forma de hablar, no sé si hay una buena traducción en su idioma."

# game/episode016.rpy:333
translate spanish ep016_prison_75a024c1:

#   xa "It’s not a literal tasting."
    xa "No es una cata literal."

# game/episode016.rpy:335
translate spanish ep016_prison_da7e6846:

#   "I did my best shaking the image of the huge snake trying to nibble on a human appendage."
    "Hice lo que pude para sacudir la imagen de la enorme serpiente intentando mordisquear un apéndice humano."

# game/episode016.rpy:336
translate spanish ep016_prison_e3046e99:

#   "The Scolguin soldier didn’t seem to be unwilling to answer me, but they were very strange indeed."
    "El soldado Scolguin no parecía no querer responderme, pero eran muy extraños."

# game/episode016.rpy:337
translate spanish ep016_prison_108a75fe:

#   "It could have been the language barrier preventing the nuances of the Scolguin speech to get through, but the Scolguin almost seemed to be in a state of delirium."
    "Puede que la barrera del idioma impidiera captar los matices del habla del escolguín, pero éste casi parecía estar en un estado de delirio."

# game/episode016.rpy:338
translate spanish ep016_prison_5b7c226e:

#   c "Are you in good health?"
    c "¿Tiene buena salud?"

# game/episode016.rpy:340
translate spanish ep016_prison_d2d8defb:

#   xa "My physical form isn’t wanting, the Rhenkoy see to that."
    xa "Mi forma física no es deficiente, los Rhenkoy se encargan de eso."

# game/episode016.rpy:341
translate spanish ep016_prison_e1065119:

#   xa "But I’m far from complete."
    xa "Pero estoy lejos de estar completo."

# game/episode016.rpy:342
translate spanish ep016_prison_06c34876:

#   xa "Far from complete..."
    xa "Lejos de ser completa..."

# game/episode016.rpy:343
translate spanish ep016_prison_05799ec4:

#   xa "I need more, I deserve more."
    xa "Necesito más, merezco más."

# game/episode016.rpy:344
translate spanish ep016_prison_0e2f2297:

#   c "And what do you deserve, actually?"
    c "¿Y qué te mereces, en realidad?"

# game/episode016.rpy:346
translate spanish ep016_prison_6e67b209:

#   xa "The fruits of the mind, the nectar of the sensation!"
    xa "¡Los frutos de la mente, el néctar de la sensación!"

# game/episode016.rpy:347
translate spanish ep016_prison_6224b680:

#   xa "Do you understand?"
    xa "¿Entiendes?"

# game/episode016.rpy:348
translate spanish ep016_prison_3275e9ef:

#   c "I think so."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode016.rpy:349
translate spanish ep016_prison_95f3f6c3:

#   xa "Oh yes, the more exquisite, the better."
    xa "Oh sí, cuanto más exquisito, mejor."

# game/episode016.rpy:351
translate spanish ep016_prison_0fb04a66:

#   xa "I’ve been without it for so long and the Rhenkoy will not oblige."
    xa "Llevo mucho tiempo sin él y el Rhenkoy no quiere complacerme."

# game/episode016.rpy:352
translate spanish ep016_prison_e9dd6121:

#   c "Maybe I can arrange something."
    c "Quizá pueda organizar algo."

# game/episode016.rpy:354
translate spanish ep016_prison_32622f99:

#   xa "You can?"
    xa "¿Puedes?"

# game/episode016.rpy:355
translate spanish ep016_prison_05b27c47:

#   c "What does the process entail, how will you “taste”?"
    c "¿En qué consiste el proceso, cómo se \"saborea\"?"

# game/episode016.rpy:357
translate spanish ep016_prison_b3c4d962:

#   xa "There’s a ritual we perform, a merging of minds."
    xa "Hay un ritual que realizamos, una fusión de mentes."

# game/episode016.rpy:358
translate spanish ep016_prison_6ee83e51:

#   xa "You will open yourself to me and I will taste everything you’ve experienced."
    xa "Te abrirás a mí y saborearé todo lo que has experimentado."

# game/episode016.rpy:359
translate spanish ep016_prison_45570a4d:

#   xa "Please, let me drink."
    xa "Por favor, déjame beber."

# game/episode016.rpy:360
translate spanish ep016_prison_636554ac:

#   c "I think not."
    c "Creo que no."

# game/episode016.rpy:361
translate spanish ep016_prison_a19f51c1:

#   xa "You want something in return, of course."
    xa "Quieres algo a cambio, por supuesto."

# game/episode016.rpy:363
translate spanish ep016_prison_695cfc8e:

#   xa "A trade?"
    xa "¿Un intercambio?"

# game/episode016.rpy:364
translate spanish ep016_prison_3db3d4d6:

#   c "I’m not going to let you rape my mind just to get a fix."
    c "No voy a dejar que violes mi mente sólo para conseguir una dosis."

# game/episode016.rpy:366
translate spanish ep016_prison_c86b787d:

#   xa "There can be boundaries..."
    xa "Puede haber límites..."

# game/episode016.rpy:367
translate spanish ep016_prison_be38bc67:

#   c "Here’s the deal, I give you one experience, something which will make you last a long time."
    c "Este es el trato, te doy una experiencia, algo que te hará durar mucho tiempo."

# game/episode016.rpy:368
translate spanish ep016_prison_796fd3f1:

#   c "In return you give me a way to establish direct contact with the Scolguin mother fleet."
    c "A cambio me das una forma de establecer contacto directo con la flota nodriza Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:370
translate spanish ep016_prison_a5ede09a:

#   xa "I can’t give up that kind of information."
    xa "No puedo dar ese tipo de información."

# game/episode016.rpy:371
translate spanish ep016_prison_a91fe642:

#   c "That’s a shame, because in that case you’ll be living off the Rhenkoy hospitality for the rest of your miserable life."
    c "Es una pena, porque en ese caso vivirás de la hospitalidad Rhenkoy el resto de tu miserable vida."

# game/episode016.rpy:373
translate spanish ep016_prison_f8afcc78:

#   xa "But what if I don’t know of a way to establish contact?"
    xa "Pero, ¿y si no sé cómo establecer contacto?"

# game/episode016.rpy:374
translate spanish ep016_prison_f071dab0:

#   c "Don’t bother, your first response gave you away immediately."
    c "No te molestes, tu primera respuesta te delató inmediatamente."

# game/episode016.rpy:375
translate spanish ep016_prison_e8b84cb9:

#   c "So, what will it be?"
    c "Entonces, ¿qué será?"

# game/episode016.rpy:377
translate spanish ep016_prison_5aa4b41a:

#   "The Scolguin regarded me silently, her impassive gaze not giving away much."
    "La Scolguin me miró en silencio, su mirada impasible no delataba gran cosa."

# game/episode016.rpy:378
translate spanish ep016_prison_670e73aa:

#   "The length of her silence gave me the impression she was carefully weighing her options though."
    "La duración de su silencio me dio la impresión de que estaba sopesando cuidadosamente sus opciones."

# game/episode016.rpy:379
translate spanish ep016_prison_8c944b72:

#   c "Time to make a decision, otherwise I’ll have to see if one of your squad-mates is more eager to make a deal."
    c "Es hora de tomar una decisión, de lo contrario tendré que ver si alguno de tus compañeros tiene más ganas de llegar a un acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:381
translate spanish ep016_prison_a447eb50:

#   xa "No!"
    xa "¡No!"

# game/episode016.rpy:383
translate spanish ep016_prison_7145fe21:

#   xa "The trade is...{w} Fair..."
    xa "El comercio es...{w} Justo..."

# game/episode016.rpy:387
translate spanish ep016_prison_139c6bba:

#   c "Good."
    c "Bien."

# game/episode016.rpy:388
translate spanish ep016_prison_29b93291:

#   c "So how do we do this?"
    c "¿Cómo lo hacemos?"

# game/episode016.rpy:390
translate spanish ep016_prison_2c3c89c0:

#   xa "We will have to attune ourselves to each other, in order for me to fully share your experiences."
    xa "Tendremos que sintonizarnos para que pueda compartir plenamente sus experiencias."

# game/episode016.rpy:391
translate spanish ep016_prison_5e5c0940:

#   c "Just this one experience."
    c "Sólo esta experiencia."

# game/episode016.rpy:393
translate spanish ep016_prison_f2a38af8:

#   xa "Yes, I will not overstep the bounds we have agreed upon."
    xa "Sí, no traspasaré los límites que hemos acordado."

# game/episode016.rpy:394
translate spanish ep016_prison_7d6f95d6:

#   c "How do we attune?"
    c "¿Cómo sintonizamos?"

# game/episode016.rpy:395
translate spanish ep016_prison_6ac49735:

#   xa "Just listen intently."
    xa "Sólo escucha atentamente."

# game/episode016.rpy:397
translate spanish ep016_prison_38c145df:

#   "As Xatrape was silent after that, listening seemed a little redundant."
    "Como Xatrape se quedó en silencio después de eso, escuchar parecía un poco redundante."

# game/episode016.rpy:398
translate spanish ep016_prison_07efd9b4:

#   "Just as I was about to make a snide comment, I could feel something probing the fringes of my thoughts."
    "Justo cuando iba a hacer un comentario sarcástico, sentí que algo sondeaba los límites de mis pensamientos."

# game/episode016.rpy:399
translate spanish ep016_prison_2965f3cb:

#   xa "You are resisting."
    xa "Te estás resistiendo."

# game/episode016.rpy:400
translate spanish ep016_prison_c03e8ad1:

#   "Before she told me, I didn’t know I was."
    "Antes de que me lo dijera, no sabía que lo era."

# game/episode016.rpy:401
translate spanish ep016_prison_f6b8ecec:

#   "And suddenly a different thought hit me, this felt exactly the same as when the Scolguin ship hit me with their laser beam."
    "Y de repente un pensamiento diferente me golpeó, esto se sentía exactamente igual que cuando la nave Scolguin me golpeó con su rayo láser."

# game/episode016.rpy:402
translate spanish ep016_prison_e4345a0c:

#   "I didn’t realize it at the time, probably because of all the near-death panic going on, but the ship probably probed me as Xatrape was doing now."
    "No me di cuenta en ese momento, probablemente por todo el pánico a la muerte que estaba pasando, pero la nave probablemente me sondeó como Xatrape estaba haciendo ahora."

# game/episode016.rpy:403
translate spanish ep016_prison_1dda240f:

#   c "This is what you do to the sacrificial victims you request."
    c "Esto es lo que haces a las víctimas sacrificiales que solicitas."

# game/episode016.rpy:405
translate spanish ep016_prison_9e8c4d4f:

#   xa "This is how we Taste the Offerings, yes."
    xa "Así es como probamos las ofrendas, sí."

# game/episode016.rpy:406
translate spanish ep016_prison_ede37f9e:

#   xa "You are still resisting."
    xa "Sigues resistiéndote."

# game/episode016.rpy:407
translate spanish ep016_prison_96e82aa0:

#   c "Sorry, attempted brain molestation generally has that effect on me..."
    c "Lo siento, el intento de abuso cerebral generalmente tiene ese efecto en mí..."

# game/episode016.rpy:409
translate spanish ep016_prison_86a5fef5:

#   "Xatrape gave me a withering look and I made a new attempt to let her in."
    "Xatrape me lanzó una mirada fulminante y yo hice un nuevo intento de dejarla pasar."

# game/episode016.rpy:410
translate spanish ep016_prison_46d94ca8:

#   "I could feel her questing out again and envisioned an opening in my thoughts."
    "Podía sentir su búsqueda de nuevo y vislumbré una abertura en mis pensamientos."

# game/episode016.rpy:411
translate spanish ep016_prison_613c45e1:

#   "She immediately pushed through and I could suddenly feel her hunger, her desire to go in completely and dominate my mind."
    "Inmediatamente empujó a través y de repente pude sentir su hambre, su deseo de entrar completamente y dominar mi mente."

# game/episode016.rpy:412
translate spanish ep016_prison_955617f4:

#   "The Scolguin restrained herself and she went no further."
    "La Scolguin se contuvo y no fue más allá."

# game/episode016.rpy:414
translate spanish ep016_prison_ed191c65:

#   xa "We are now one."
    xa "Ahora somos uno."

# game/episode016.rpy:416
translate spanish ep016_prison_d8ea15f2:

#   "Having received the information that we needed, I entered the antechamber and knocked on the outer cell door again."
    "Tras recibir la información que necesitábamos, entré en la antecámara y volví a llamar a la puerta de la celda exterior."

# game/episode016.rpy:418
translate spanish ep016_prison_716b4b92:

#   xa "Thank you for allowing me the experience."
    xa "Gracias por permitirme vivir esta experiencia."

# game/episode016.rpy:419
translate spanish ep016_prison_78292c05:

#   xa "I will cherish this for a long time."
    xa "Lo guardaré durante mucho tiempo."

# game/episode016.rpy:421
translate spanish ep016_prison_66bdbf2b:

#   "Suppressing a slight shiver, I shook off the last remnants of her mental connection and stepped out into the light."
    "Reprimiendo un ligero escalofrío, me deshice de los últimos restos de su conexión mental y salí a la luz."

# game/episode016.rpy:434
translate spanish ep016_prison_3200e9a6:

#   "The others were looking at me expectantly."
    "Los demás me miraban expectantes."

# game/episode016.rpy:435
translate spanish ep016_prison_4932768a:

#   c "I think we got what we came for."
    c "Creo que tenemos lo que buscábamos."

# game/episode016.rpy:436
translate spanish ep016_prison_c2dff550:

#   c "Thank you for your cooperation, we will be returning to the transport and back to our ship."
    c "Gracias por su cooperación, volveremos al transporte y a nuestra nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:438
translate spanish ep016_prison_e958576d:

#   woman "Of course, we will escort you to the landing pad."
    woman "Por supuesto, le escoltaremos hasta la pista de aterrizaje."

# game/episode016.rpy:440
translate spanish ep016_prison_38a6c121:

#   "When the guards had dropped us off at the shuttle, we dawdled a little in front of the craft."
    "Cuando los guardias nos dejaron en la lanzadera, nos entretuvimos un poco delante de la nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:442
translate spanish ep016_prison_09b3c7eb:

#   na "Did you learn anything?"
    na "¿Has aprendido algo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:443
translate spanish ep016_prison_6495739b:

#   c "Yes, she showed me the way to gain access to the Scolguin fleet."
    c "Sí, ella me mostró el camino para acceder a la flota Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:444
translate spanish ep016_prison_2c2fc864:

#   c "We are to travel to a place called the Supplicant’s Stone."
    c "Debemos viajar a un lugar llamado la Piedra del Suplicante."

# game/episode016.rpy:445
translate spanish ep016_prison_ada2cdd2:

#   c "Traditionally, anyone who wants something from the Scolguin leaves their sacrifices there."
