# game/episode016.rpy:625
translate spanish ep016_prison_af88d72e:

#   ki "Oh, she tried, but I kept her out of it."
    ki "Lo intentó, pero la mantuve al margen."

# game/episode016.rpy:626
translate spanish ep016_prison_15c21326:

#   ki "And then we fucked."
    ki "Y luego follamos."

# game/episode016.rpy:627
translate spanish ep016_prison_d952ae4b:

#   ki "You know why I don’t doubt she told me the truth about those coordinates and the radio frequency?"
    ki "¿Sabes por qué no dudo de que me dijo la verdad sobre esas coordenadas y la frecuencia de radio?"

# game/episode016.rpy:629
translate spanish ep016_prison_39e8e92b:

#   ki "She never spoke about them, but showed them in my mind while she had a major orgasm."
    ki "Nunca hablaba de ellos, pero los mostraba en mi mente mientras tenía un gran orgasmo."

# game/episode016.rpy:630
translate spanish ep016_prison_f488f75f:

#   c "Sounds like you had a fun time."
    c "Parece que te lo has pasado bien."

# game/episode016.rpy:631
translate spanish ep016_prison_ba1cb900:

#   ki "I sure did."
    ki "Claro que sí."

# game/episode016.rpy:633
translate spanish ep016_prison_ce9c6d36:

#   ki "One more item to strike off my bucket list."
    ki "Otra cosa más que tachar de mi lista de cosas que hacer antes de morir."

# game/episode016.rpy:634
translate spanish ep016_prison_6646de20:

#   c "I wonder what’s on that list sometimes and then I realize I might not want to know."
    c "A veces me pregunto qué hay en esa lista y luego me doy cuenta de que quizá no quiera saberlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:635
translate spanish ep016_prison_6a49f34c:

#   ki "Haha, fuck you."
    ki "Jaja, vete a la mierda."

# game/episode016.rpy:636
translate spanish ep016_prison_4ab01a29:

#   ki "Let’s not keep Nadya waiting."
    ki "No hagamos esperar a Nadya."

# game/episode016.rpy:651
translate spanish ep016_prison_dfe424ad:

#   "Back on the ship we brought everyone up to speed."
    "De vuelta al barco, pusimos a todo el mundo al día."

# game/episode016.rpy:654
translate spanish ep016_prison_aecaf233:

#   "Most of the crew were fine with the plan to fly out to the Supplicant’s Stone, but my mother and sisters lingered after the briefing."
    "A la mayoría de la tripulación le pareció bien el plan de volar hasta la Piedra del Suplicante, pero mi madre y mis hermanas se quedaron después de la sesión informativa."

# game/episode016.rpy:656
translate spanish ep016_prison_764da447:

#   "Most of the crew were fine with the plan to fly out to the Supplicant’s Stone, but Eva, Lilly, Aven and Nadya lingered after the briefing."
    "La mayoría de la tripulación estaba de acuerdo con el plan de volar hasta la Piedra del Suplicante, pero Eva, Lilly, Aven y Nadya se quedaron después de la reunión informativa."

# game/episode016.rpy:658
translate spanish ep016_prison_ce8027c3:

#   e "So, are we sure we want to do this?"
    e "Entonces, ¿estamos seguros de que queremos hacerlo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:659
translate spanish ep016_prison_26bfc3a0:

#   e "Are you sure you’re up for it, [p_name_short]?"
    e "¿Seguro que te apetece, [p_name_short]?"

# game/episode016.rpy:660
translate spanish ep016_prison_94878a68:

#   c "Why wouldn’t I be?"
    c "¿Por qué no iba a estarlo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:662
translate spanish ep016_prison_7b734aa9:

#   av "Well, you were the one who was used by the Scolguin before."
    av "Bueno, tú fuiste el que fue utilizado por el Scolguin antes."

# game/episode016.rpy:663
translate spanish ep016_prison_93e39793:

#   c "I mostly blame my father for that, the Scolguin were just doing what they always do, apparently."
    c "Culpo sobre todo a mi padre por eso, los Scolguin sólo estaban haciendo lo que siempre hacen, aparentemente."

# game/episode016.rpy:665
translate spanish ep016_prison_72643481:

#   l "I’m sure that’s true, but if it all works, we’ll be heading straight into the Scolguin mother fleet."
    l "Estoy seguro de que es cierto, pero si todo funciona, nos dirigiremos directamente a la flota nodriza Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:666
translate spanish ep016_prison_750a2e12:

#   l "Who knows what they’ll do to us?"
    l "¿Quién sabe lo que nos harán?"

# game/episode016.rpy:667
translate spanish ep016_prison_86e6e254:

#   c "There is a risk, but we cannot wander aimlessly through the galaxy either."
    c "Existe un riesgo, pero tampoco podemos vagar sin rumbo por la galaxia."

# game/episode016.rpy:669
translate spanish ep016_prison_743b3df8:

#   na "We could pilot a shuttle with a skeleton crew towards the Supplicant’s Stone and leave the Bastard at a safer distance."
    na "Podríamos pilotar una lanzadera con una tripulación esquelética hacia la Piedra del Suplicante y dejar al Bastardo a una distancia más segura."

# game/episode016.rpy:670
translate spanish ep016_prison_aeabf9ca:

#   c "There are two problems with that."
    c "Esto plantea dos problemas."

# game/episode016.rpy:671
translate spanish ep016_prison_a7fe0f19:

#   c "We don’t have a shuttle and any shuttle is likely going to be less well-armed than the Bastard is."
    c "No tenemos un transbordador y cualquier transbordador probablemente estará menos armado que el Bastardo."

# game/episode016.rpy:672
translate spanish ep016_prison_42f575b4:

#   l "It’s too dangerous."
    l "Es demasiado peligroso."

# game/episode016.rpy:674
translate spanish ep016_prison_bcfeb3ad:

#   e "We’ve done worse and this is the most tangible lead we have."
    e "Hemos hecho cosas peores y esta es la pista más tangible que tenemos."

# game/episode016.rpy:675
translate spanish ep016_prison_ccf7ed73:

#   c "If we are attacked, we could always Burst our Drive as a last resort."
    c "Si nos atacan, siempre podemos hacer estallar nuestra unidad como último recurso."

# game/episode016.rpy:677
translate spanish ep016_prison_1fbd6e7e:

#   l "That may have worked the last time, but there’s no telling it will now."
    l "Puede que funcionara la última vez, pero no se sabe si lo hará ahora."

# game/episode016.rpy:678
translate spanish ep016_prison_d47029b4:

#   c "I’m not denying there’s a risk, but it’s one we have to take."
    c "No niego que haya un riesgo, pero hay que asumirlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:680
translate spanish ep016_prison_9318b9dd:

#   l "I just wish we didn’t have to do all this anymore."
    l "Ojalá no tuviéramos que hacer todo esto nunca más."

# game/episode016.rpy:681
translate spanish ep016_prison_1037b4aa:

#   l "I wish we could just get on and live our lives."
    l "Ojalá pudiéramos seguir adelante y vivir nuestras vidas."

# game/episode016.rpy:683
translate spanish ep016_prison_8772e807:

#   e "That’s the reason we’re doing this, Lilly."
    e "Esa es la razón por la que estamos haciendo esto, Lilly."

# game/episode016.rpy:684
translate spanish ep016_prison_2ff15d56:

#   e "We won’t know peace until Agust and the others stop their search for us."
    e "No conoceremos la paz hasta que Agust y los otros dejen de buscarnos."

# game/episode016.rpy:685
translate spanish ep016_prison_f50c1b6a:

#   "Nadya, Aven and Lilly relented in the end."
    "Al final, Nadya, Aven y Lilly cedieron."

# game/episode016.rpy:687
translate spanish ep016_prison_a1a75897:

#   "An hour later, Céline set course to the system where the Supplicant’s Stone was supposed to be."
    "Una hora más tarde, Céline puso rumbo al sistema donde se suponía que estaba la Piedra del Suplicante."

# game/episode016.rpy:520
translate spanish ep016_prison_8259ef80_1:

#   ki "Right."
    ki "Bien."

# game/episode016.rpy:638
translate spanish ep016_prison_0d360386_1:

#   "We went up into the shuttle and traveled back to the Bastard."
    "Subimos al transbordador y viajamos de vuelta al Bastardo."

# game/episode016.rpy:697
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9fef67b9:

#   "The system where the Scolguin rallying beacon could be found was relatively unassuming."
    "El sistema en el que se encontraba la baliza de reunión Scolguin era relativamente sencillo."

# game/episode016.rpy:698
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cee98231:

#   "As the system wasn’t very stable, only short visits were possible."
    "Como el sistema no era muy estable, sólo se podían hacer visitas cortas."

# game/episode016.rpy:699
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_853c6ef1:

#   "Any form of long-term mining was out of the question and there were no habitable planets in the area."
    "Cualquier forma de explotación minera a largo plazo estaba descartada y no había planetas habitables en la zona."

# game/episode016.rpy:701
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b555bb74:

#   "The only thing of interest was a medium-sized asteroid, dubbed the Supplicant’s Stone."
    "Lo único de interés era un asteroide de tamaño medio, bautizado como la Piedra del Suplicante."

# game/episode016.rpy:702
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3e8daefe:

#   "We approached the Scolguin rallying beacon at a slow burn, scanners at maximum sensitivity."
    "Nos acercamos a la baliza de reunión Scolguin a fuego lento, con los escáneres al máximo de sensibilidad."

# game/episode016.rpy:704
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5a5eaf83:

#   c "Ready to broadcast that signal?"
    c "¿Listo para emitir esa señal?"

# game/episode016.rpy:705
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0054f605:

#   ce "I am."
    ce "Lo soy."

# game/episode016.rpy:706
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_011079c4:

#   c "Do it."
    c "Hazlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:708
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_8bcbb2bb:

#   "The signal went out and we waited."
    "La señal se apagó y esperamos."

# game/episode016.rpy:709
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b8652d40:

#   "It didn’t take long before our sensors picked up multiple vessels."
    "Nuestros sensores no tardaron en detectar varias naves."

# game/episode016.rpy:711
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_028376a0:

#   "Sirens started blaring as we were targeted by several ships surrounding the Bastard."
    "Las sirenas comenzaron a sonar mientras éramos blanco de varios barcos que rodeaban al Bastardo."

# game/episode016.rpy:712
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b5b5959e:

#   "The ships looked distinctly like the one that had scanned me, so I knew for certain the Scolguin had arrived."
    "Las naves se parecían mucho a la que me había escaneado, así que supe con certeza que el Scolguin había llegado."

# game/episode016.rpy:714
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9e0946ba:

#   ce "They’re hailing us."
    ce "Nos están llamando."

# game/episode016.rpy:715
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_624bee8f:

#   c "Put them through."
    c "Pásalos."

# game/episode016.rpy:718
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_7729901e:

#   man "Unknown vessel, you are not authorized to pay tribute at the Supplicant’s Stone."
    man "Buque desconocido, no estás autorizado a pagar tributo en la Piedra del Suplicante."

# game/episode016.rpy:719
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_132c5766:

#   man "We will proceed to destroy your vessel."
    man "Procederemos a destruir su nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:721
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b437b351:

#   c "Fuck."
    c "Joder."

# game/episode016.rpy:722
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_471d1f1b:

#   c "Burst us out of here!"
    c "¡Sácanos de aquí!"

# game/episode016.rpy:723
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e2de9c63:

#   ce "On it, try to stall them."
    ce "En él, intenta entretenerlos."

# game/episode016.rpy:725
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bcd3335f:

#   c "Scolguin fleet, this is the Captain of the Iron Bastard, we have arrived here with a proposal for your leader."
    c "Flota Scolguin, aquí el Capitán del Bastardo de Hierro, hemos llegado con una propuesta para su líder."

# game/episode016.rpy:726
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ef3b291b:

#   "The Scolguin didn’t respond."
    "El Scolguin no respondió."

# game/episode016.rpy:727
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_94ad7e55:

#   c "Are their weapons hot?"
    c "¿Están calientes sus armas?"

# game/episode016.rpy:729
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_7ea933b6:

#   ce "They’re still powering up, I think."
    ce "Creo que todavía se están encendiendo."

# game/episode016.rpy:730
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5c0a2c57:

#   ce "We’re still being targeted."
    ce "Seguimos siendo un objetivo."

# game/episode016.rpy:731
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9898b974:

#   c "How long before we can Burst?"
    c "¿Cuánto falta para que podamos estallar?"

# game/episode016.rpy:732
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b84174fc:

#   ce "One minute."
    ce "Un minuto."

# game/episode016.rpy:734
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3a166f73:

#   c "This is the Captain of the Iron Bastard, Scolguin fleet, do you copy?"
    c "Este es el Capitán del Bastardo de Hierro, flota Scolguin, ¿me copia?"

# game/episode016.rpy:735
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bec3b8d3:

#   "There were still thirty seconds on the clock and I was beginning to despair we’d just be annihilated at some lonely anonymous rock when the comms crackled."
    "Todavía quedaban treinta segundos en el reloj y empezaba a desesperar de que nos aniquilaran en alguna roca solitaria y anónima cuando crepitó el comunicador."

# game/episode016.rpy:737
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_8eef92b8:

#   man "Captain of the Iron Bastard, we have received your message."
    man "Capitán del Bastardo de Hierro, hemos recibido su mensaje."

# game/episode016.rpy:738
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9c1bb1f7:

#   "The Scolguin liaison was still talking when Céline indicated that we would be able to Burst at will."
    "El enlace de Scolguin seguía hablando cuando Céline indicó que podríamos reventar a voluntad."

# game/episode016.rpy:739
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ac753c19:

#   "I motioned her to hold off and focused my attention on the Scolguin."
    "Le hice un gesto para que se contuviera y centré mi atención en el Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:740
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f3adfb8a:

#   man "We have just been ordered to halt the destruction of your vessel."
    man "Nos acaban de ordenar que detengamos la destrucción de su nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:741
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_de15d3a1:

#   man "It seems that Her Majesty is interested in you and has granted an audience."
    man "Parece que Su Majestad está interesada en usted y le ha concedido una audiencia."

# game/episode016.rpy:742
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_103c7a1e:

#   man "Please follow the path as indicated by the guiding beacons."
    man "Siga el camino indicado por las balizas."

# game/episode016.rpy:744
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d0e632cc:

#   ce "The Scolguin have a queen?"
    ce "¿Los Scolguin tienen reina?"

# game/episode016.rpy:745
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5a04b24f:

#   c "Apparently so."
    c "Eso parece."

# game/episode016.rpy:746
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a8786427:

#   ce "And she has an interest in you...{w} that can't be healthy."
    ce "Y ella tiene un interés en ti ... {w} que no puede ser saludable."

# game/episode016.rpy:747
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_72cfe8d2:

#   c "You know I always like to have an optimistic outlook on things, but I agree."
    c "Ya sabes que siempre me gusta tener una visión optimista de las cosas, pero estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:748
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5232b905:

#   c "But we're here now, so let's make the best of it."
    c "Pero ya estamos aquí, así que aprovechémoslo."

# game/episode016.rpy:753
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_409410ea:

#   "Céline flew us along the guiding beacons towards one of the larger ships in the Scolguin fleet."
    "Céline nos llevó por las balizas de guía hacia uno de los barcos más grandes de la flota Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:755
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bb77eedf:

#   "Blinking lights marked the way inside the belly of the large ship."
    "Las luces parpadeantes marcaban el camino hacia el interior del vientre de la gran nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:757
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_10f98c25:

#   "We landed in its hangar bay where several other ships were housed."
    "Aterrizamos en su hangar, donde se encontraban otras naves."

# game/episode016.rpy:759
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a8357c99:

#   "A contingent of Scolguin warriors was already waiting for us when we opened our doors."
    "Un contingente de guerreros escolguines ya nos esperaba cuando abrimos nuestras puertas."

# game/episode016.rpy:760
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5b89c15f:

#   "Nadya, Aven and Kit had asked to accompany me to my audience with the Scolguin queen."
    "Nadya, Aven y Kit habían pedido acompañarme a mi audiencia con la reina Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:762
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9cecffb3:

#   "Surrounded by warriors, we made our way through the ship."
    "Rodeados de guerreros, nos abrimos paso por la nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:764
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_62d64ff5:

#   "While I was merely wary of my surrounding, Nadya seemed to take it all in with the analytical eye of the scientist that she was."
    "Mientras yo me limitaba a desconfiar de lo que me rodeaba, Nadya parecía asimilarlo todo con la mirada analítica de la científica que era."

# game/episode016.rpy:765
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a227c007:

#   "The Scolguin didn't display much skill as interior decorators, unless drab colors and slimy webs were one of the trendy hallmarks of the current fashion."
    "Los Scolguin no demostraron mucha habilidad como decoradores de interiores, a menos que los colores monótonos y las telarañas viscosas fueran una de las señas de identidad de la moda del momento."

# game/episode016.rpy:766
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e48681dc:

#   "The throne room appeared to be in the heart of the enormous ship."
    "La sala del trono parecía estar en el corazón de la enorme nave."

# game/episode016.rpy:768
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_97cdfd4d:

#   "A large throne-like object stood in the middle of a garden of glowing plants."
    "Un gran objeto parecido a un trono se erguía en medio de un jardín de plantas resplandecientes."

# game/episode016.rpy:769
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_85f36f3c:

#   "The Scolguin queen was draped on the throne and looked at us through the gloom."
    "La reina Scolguin estaba sentada en el trono y nos miraba a través de la penumbra."

# game/episode016.rpy:772
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_23e7a0c3:

#   woman "Welcome, [p_name]."
    woman "Bienvenido, [p_name]."

# game/episode016.rpy:773
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_2c689836:

#   "The fact that she already knew my name didn't really put me at ease."
    "El hecho de que ya supiera mi nombre no me tranquilizó."

# game/episode016.rpy:774
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_74a9437e:

#   c "The honor is all mine, your highness."
    c "El honor es todo mío, su alteza."

# game/episode016.rpy:775
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_1a2f4ad8:

#   woman "You are such an interesting little human."
    woman "Eres un pequeño humano tan interesante."

# game/episode016.rpy:776
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cfa671b1:

#   "I wasn't sure a response was expected, so instead I let the Scolguin Queen continue to play out that whole creepy alien shtick."
    "No estaba segura de que esperara una respuesta, así que dejé que la Reina Escolapio siguiera con su espeluznante numerito alienígena."

# game/episode016.rpy:777
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_01322afc:

#   woman "You see, I know all about you."
    woman "Verás, lo sé todo sobre ti."

# game/episode016.rpy:780
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_6fb8b482:

#   woman "The desertion, searching for your sister, the joy you felt when you found her."
    woman "La deserción, la búsqueda de tu hermana, la alegría que sentiste cuando la encontraste."

# game/episode016.rpy:782
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_03dde59f:

#   woman "The desertion, searching for your friend, the joy you felt when you found her."
    woman "La deserción, la búsqueda de su amiga, la alegría que sintió cuando la encontró."

# game/episode016.rpy:783
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_81888803:

#   woman "And the women you lusted over, oh the great many women!"
    woman "Y las mujeres que deseaste, ¡oh, la gran cantidad de mujeres!"

# game/episode016.rpy:784
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4c932b2e:

#   c "Ah, you're referring to the memories that were stolen from me as I drifted helplessly through space?"
    c "Ah, ¿te refieres a los recuerdos que me robaron mientras vagaba indefenso por el espacio?"

# game/episode016.rpy:786
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5e6cc9d1:

#   woman "None of the Offerings that were gifted to us to Taste have survived."
    woman "Ninguna de las Ofrendas que se nos regalaron para Degustar ha sobrevivido."

# game/episode016.rpy:787
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f653feff:

#   woman "That makes you unique."
    woman "Eso te hace único."

# game/episode016.rpy:788
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_21a3e20d:

#   c "I feel very special."
    c "Me siento muy especial."

# game/episode016.rpy:789
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f7e054a8:

#   "The Queen either missed the sarcasm dripping from my voice, or she chose to ignore it."
    "La Reina no percibió el sarcasmo que destilaba mi voz o prefirió ignorarlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:790
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3d5dee3a:

#   woman "Come closer, please."
    woman "Acércate, por favor."

# game/episode016.rpy:791
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_740a24a4:

#   "I approached the Scolguin Queen while the others waited further back."
    "Me acerqué a la Reina Escolapia mientras los demás esperaban más atrás."

# game/episode016.rpy:794
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5725e5df:

#   "The Queen’s voice dropped to a conspirational tone when she next spoke."
    "La voz de la Reina bajó a un tono de conspiración cuando habló a continuación."

# game/episode016.rpy:795
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_79c686ea:

#   woman "Tell me [p_name], does every one of your species desire their own family?"
    woman "Dime [p_name], ¿cada uno de tu especie desea su propia familia?"

# game/episode016.rpy:796
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_7a46c418:

#   c "I’m sure there are more than dare to agree."
    c "Seguro que hay más de uno que se atreve a estar de acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:797
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4b02177c:

#   "The Queen smiled, apparently satisfied by my answer."
    "La Reina sonrió, aparentemente satisfecha por mi respuesta."

# game/episode016.rpy:798
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3b249b52:

#   woman "Why have you come here, what do you desire of us?"
    woman "¿Por qué has venido aquí, qué deseas de nosotros?"

# game/episode016.rpy:799
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cf97bb3e:

#   c "The deal you’ve struck with my father, the one who tossed me out into space, I want to know what he knows."
    c "El trato que has hecho con mi padre, el que me lanzó al espacio, quiero saber lo que sabe."

# game/episode016.rpy:801
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3e358d59:

#   woman "You desire the knowledge sought by your father?"
    woman "¿Deseas el conocimiento que buscaba tu padre?"

# game/episode016.rpy:802
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e7dd5805:

#   c "I do, your highness."
    c "Sí, su alteza."

# game/episode016.rpy:804
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f9bdb237:

#   woman "The sacrificial contract between the Scolguin Empire and Supplicant is sacred and confidential."
    woman "El contrato de sacrificio entre el Imperio Escolguín y Suplicante es sagrado y confidencial."

# game/episode016.rpy:805
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9463b948:

#   c "I’m sure it is, but I believe we can come to an arrangement."
    c "Seguro que sí, pero creo que podemos llegar a un acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:806
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_df486e05:

#   woman "We can?"
    woman "¿Podemos?"

# game/episode016.rpy:808
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f97af5d5:

#   woman "Such confidence."
    woman "Tanta confianza."

# game/episode016.rpy:810
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0dc64703:

#   woman "What do you offer?"
    woman "¿Qué ofrece?"

# game/episode016.rpy:811
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_105a5b33:

#   "The Scolguin Queen didn’t shut me down immediately, which made me wonder just how sacred and confidential those contracts actually were."
    "La Reina Escolapia no me cerró el grifo de inmediato, lo que me hizo preguntarme hasta qué punto eran sagrados y confidenciales esos contratos."

# game/episode016.rpy:812
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_15115588:

#   "Nevertheless, I felt I needed to offer her something substantial."
    "Sin embargo, sentí que debía ofrecerle algo sustancial."

# game/episode016.rpy:813
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_2015eb64:

#   c "Your Highness has already expressed her intrigue regarding my life."
    c "Su Alteza ya ha expresado su intriga sobre mi vida."

# game/episode016.rpy:814
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f33a698a:

#   c "And whatever else you can say about my life so far, it has certainly been interesting."
    c "Y cualquier otra cosa que se pueda decir de mi vida hasta ahora, sin duda ha sido interesante."

# game/episode016.rpy:815
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0e954944:

#   c "I’m fairly confident it will remain interesting for the foreseeable future."
    c "Estoy bastante seguro de que seguirá siendo interesante en un futuro próximo."

# game/episode016.rpy:816
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_dcccd0bf:

#   c "So I’m offering you the experiences of my life for the next ten years."
    c "Así que te ofrezco las experiencias de mi vida durante los próximos diez años."

# game/episode016.rpy:818
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_11b72724:

#   c "We trade the information my father received and then I will leave, to return in ten years time to subject myself to whatever mind rape needed to extract the new memories I’ve made."
    c "Intercambiamos la información que recibió mi padre y luego me iré, para volver dentro de diez años y someterme a cualquier violación mental necesaria para extraer los nuevos recuerdos que he creado."

# game/episode016.rpy:819
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0987115f:

#   "I heard gasping behind my back and the Queen regarded me in silence."
    "Oí jadeos a mis espaldas y la Reina me miró en silencio."

# game/episode016.rpy:820
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4b658f36:

#   "When she spoke again, I could see the hungry glitter in her eyes."
    "Cuando volvió a hablar, pude ver el brillo hambriento en sus ojos."

# game/episode016.rpy:821
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_17d9cb13:

#   woman "An enticing promise."
    woman "Una promesa tentadora."

# game/episode016.rpy:823
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a7e1e220:

#   woman "How will you keep it?"
    woman "¿Cómo lo conservará?"

# game/episode016.rpy:824
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_022e0a78:

#   c "I’m willing to offer it in writing, or by any other means you deem satisfactory."
    c "Estoy dispuesto a ofrecértelo por escrito o por cualquier otro medio que consideres satisfactorio."

# game/episode016.rpy:825
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d6b7e9fa:

#   woman "But what if you die before the ten years are out?"
    woman "Pero, ¿y si mueres antes de que pasen los diez años?"

# game/episode016.rpy:826
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_dadeb206:

#   c "That is a risk you have to take, your highness."
    c "Es un riesgo que debe correr, su alteza."

# game/episode016.rpy:827
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e05254fd:

#   c "I can only promise I will return in ten years, my untimely death is something I’d like to avoid as well, so we have a mutual interest in that regard."
    c "Sólo puedo prometer que volveré dentro de diez años, mi muerte prematura es algo que también me gustaría evitar, así que tenemos un interés mutuo en ese sentido."

# game/episode016.rpy:829
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b29cfea8:

#   woman "An alluring offer, which the Scolguin Empire accepts."
    woman "Una oferta seductora, que el Imperio Scolguin acepta."

# game/episode016.rpy:830
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e4344522:

#   woman "A contract for you to sign will be drafted shortly."
    woman "En breve redactaremos un contrato para que lo firme."

# game/episode016.rpy:831
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ead546a8:

#   c "Excellent."
    c "Excelente."

# game/episode016.rpy:833
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_c7d5d277:

#   na "No!{w} Wait!"
    na "¡No!{w} ¡Espera!"

# game/episode016.rpy:835
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0fd70fb4:

#   "The obvious breach of protocol by my mother didn’t have any serious repercussions, other than startling the Queen."
    "La evidente ruptura del protocolo por parte de mi madre no tuvo ninguna repercusión grave, aparte de sobresaltar a la Reina."

# game/episode016.rpy:837
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ecc93874:

#   "The obvious breach of protocol by Nadya didn’t have any serious repercussions, other than startling the Queen."
    "La evidente ruptura del protocolo por parte de Nadya no tuvo ninguna repercusión grave, aparte de sobresaltar a la Reina."

# game/episode016.rpy:838
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e5756f7e:

#   na "Your majesty, allow me to speak on my behalf."
    na "Majestad, permítame hablar en mi nombre."

# game/episode016.rpy:839
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_075f9854:

#   woman "Approach."
    woman "Enfoque."

# game/episode016.rpy:841
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_128ba0fb:

#   "Nadya glanced at me nervously as she passed me and stood before the Queen."
    "Nadya me miró nerviosa cuando pasó junto a mí y se plantó ante la Reina."

# game/episode016.rpy:842
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cf178ab5:

#   woman "Speak."
    woman "Habla."

# game/episode016.rpy:843
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_2dd233e4:

#   na "Pick me instead, your highness."
    na "Elíjame a mí en su lugar, su alteza."

# game/episode016.rpy:844
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_22cc3232:

#   na "I’ve lived a full life and my mind is as of yet untouched by the Scolguin Taste."
    na "He vivido una vida plena y mi mente aún no ha sido tocada por el Sabor Scolguin."

# game/episode016.rpy:846
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_54fc8102:

#   woman "A virgin mind."
    woman "Una mente virgen."

# game/episode016.rpy:848
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a3b1ccfa:

#   woman "You would agree to the same deal offered by your son?"
    woman "¿Aceptaría el mismo trato ofrecido por su hijo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:850
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0c18dfd4:

#   woman "You would agree to the same deal offered by your friend?"
    woman "¿Aceptarías el mismo trato que te ofrece tu amigo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:852
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d60bb6b5:

#   na "I would."
    na "Lo haría."

# game/episode016.rpy:854
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b23fc5c5:

#   woman "Your offer is acceptable."
    woman "Su oferta es aceptable."

# game/episode016.rpy:855
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d37eea3e:

#   woman "I’ll leave it to you both to determine who will have the honor to present themselves in ten years time."
    woman "Dejaré que ustedes dos determinen quién tendrá el honor de presentarse dentro de diez años."

# game/episode016.rpy:856
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_7e0cea96:

#   woman "But make it quick, as I tire of these deliberations."
    woman "Pero que sea rápido, ya que me canso de estas deliberaciones."

# game/episode016.rpy:858
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9708c943:

#   "We sequestered ourselves in a corner of the throne room for a short, but heated debate."
    "Nos aislamos en un rincón de la sala del trono para mantener un breve pero acalorado debate."

# game/episode016.rpy:860
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_47f6f858:

#   av "What were you both thinking, offering yourselves up like that?!"
    av "¡¿En qué estaban pensando, ofreciéndose así?!"

# game/episode016.rpy:861
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_739de70d:

#   av "This is beyond stupidity."
    av "Esto va más allá de la estupidez."

# game/episode016.rpy:862
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_dfcd8949:

#   c "It’s necessary, how else are we going to find out what Agust is up to?"
    c "Es necesario, ¿de qué otra forma vamos a saber qué trama Agust?"

# game/episode016.rpy:864
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_24a6595c:

#   na "Agreed, but it shouldn’t be you."
    na "De acuerdo, pero no deberías ser tú."

# game/episode016.rpy:865
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_78c0d3b9:

#   na "You’ve suffered under the invasive Scolguin procedure already, I can’t allow you to do it a second time."
    na "Ya has sufrido con el invasivo procedimiento Scolguin, no puedo permitir que lo hagas una segunda vez."

# game/episode016.rpy:866
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_1453c6e4:

#   c "This time it’s voluntarily."
    c "Esta vez es voluntariamente."

# game/episode016.rpy:867
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cbb9c62e:

#   na "You shouldn’t be the one doing this."
    na "No deberías ser tú quien hiciera esto."

# game/episode016.rpy:869
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ce3f884b:

#   av "And you should?"
    av "¿Y deberías?"

# game/episode016.rpy:871
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ef5a2e98:

#   na "I’m the oldest member of the crew."
    na "Soy el miembro más viejo de la tripulación."

# game/episode016.rpy:872
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_cffa7a51:

#   na "I’ve lived a full life and-"
    na "He vivido una vida plena y..."

# game/episode016.rpy:874
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3db1e4f3:

#   av "Cut the crap, mother, you sound like you’re on your deathbed."
    av "Corta el rollo, madre, suenas como si estuvieras en tu lecho de muerte."

# game/episode016.rpy:876
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9682f432:

#   av "Cut the crap, Nadya, you sound like you’re on your deathbed."
    av "Corta el rollo, Nadya, suenas como si estuvieras en tu lecho de muerte."

# game/episode016.rpy:877
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0adb2a79:

#   na "It's a simple fact, Aven."
    na "Es un hecho simple, Aven."

# game/episode016.rpy:878
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bfe70646:

#   na "You all have a long life ahead of you."
    na "Todos tenéis una larga vida por delante."

# game/episode016.rpy:879
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_7d76d6d4:

#   na "Besides, it's not like the procedure will kill me."
    na "Además, no es que el procedimiento vaya a matarme."

# game/episode016.rpy:881
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_76edc4ed:

#   av "Don't you have anything to say?"
    av "¿No tienes nada que decir?"

# game/episode016.rpy:883
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_47c220a6:

#   ki "Who, me?"
    ki "¿Quién, yo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:885
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_613ae528:

#   av "No, the other silent guy in our group staring like he's just been lobotomized."
    av "No, el otro tipo silencioso de nuestro grupo mira como si le acabaran de hacer una lobotomía."

# game/episode016.rpy:887
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b4fd90e2:

#   ki "Right, well, if you put it that way, I think you're both crazy."
    ki "Correcto, bueno, si lo pones de esa manera, creo que ambos están locos."

# game/episode016.rpy:888
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_116b21df:

#   ki "[p_name_short], like you told 'her majesty' over there, you've just been mindraped and now you're asking for another round?"
    ki "[p_name_short], como le has dicho a 'su majestad' por ahí, ¿te acaban de violar la mente y ahora pides otra ronda?"

# game/episode016.rpy:889
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b21caacc:

#   ki "And you, Nadya, you're volunteering for something that's obviously so invasive."
    ki "Y tú, Nadya, te ofreces voluntaria para algo que obviamente es tan invasivo."

# game/episode016.rpy:890
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b0ddfde8:

#   c "What's your alternative then?"
    c "¿Cuál es entonces su alternativa?"

# game/episode016.rpy:892
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d50c599c:

#   av "There must be something."
    av "Tiene que haber algo."

# game/episode016.rpy:893
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d9bb5492:

#   c "This is the most solid lead we have."
    c "Esta es la pista más sólida que tenemos."

# game/episode016.rpy:894
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_57fccfcc:

#   c "The alternative is to keep flailing around in the dark and wait for either Agust or the Confessor to catch up and pulverize us."
    c "La alternativa es seguir dando tumbos en la oscuridad y esperar a que Agust o la Confesora nos alcancen y nos pulvericen."

# game/episode016.rpy:896
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f2ad077b:

#   na "Exactly."
    na "Exactamente."

# game/episode016.rpy:901
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0f4e5863:

#   "Shifting the responsibility towards Nadya seemed like the coward's way out, but her argument made sense."
    "Trasladar la responsabilidad a Nadya parecía la salida más cobarde, pero su argumento tenía sentido."

# game/episode016.rpy:902
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_c3d075b9:

#   "Ten years was a long time, long enough to maybe find a loophole to get out of this sordid deal."
    "Diez años era mucho tiempo, suficiente para quizá encontrar un resquicio para salir de este sórdido trato."

# game/episode016.rpy:903
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bd3b9cdf:

#   c "Are you sure you want to do this?"
    c "¿Seguro que quieres hacerlo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:905
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_81963ec2:

#   na "I am."
    na "Lo soy."

# game/episode016.rpy:906
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_10656a05:

#   c "In that case I'm going to allow amending the deal."
    c "En ese caso voy a permitir que se modifique el acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:907
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f8599a4f:

#   c "We'll find a way to get out of it before the ten-year term is up though."
    c "Sin embargo, encontraremos la manera de salir de él antes de que termine el plazo de diez años."

# game/episode016.rpy:909
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_11756f6f:

#   "I could see the dismay in Aven’s eyes, but when my sister next spoke, she sounded resigned."
    "Pude ver la consternación en los ojos de Aven, pero cuando mi hermana habló a continuación, sonaba resignada."

# game/episode016.rpy:911
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a8adf9e7:

#   "I could see the dismay in Aven’s eyes, but when she next spoke, she sounded resigned."
    "Pude ver la consternación en los ojos de Aven, pero cuando volvió a hablar, sonaba resignada."

# game/episode016.rpy:913
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e7f0f13b:

#   av "We simply must."
    av "Simplemente debemos hacerlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:915
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_db20d9f4:

#   na "Alright, let's do this."
    na "Muy bien, hagámoslo."

# game/episode016.rpy:916
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5d258918:

#   "We approached the Queen again."
    "Nos acercamos de nuevo a la Reina."

# game/episode016.rpy:918
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_8c8b89d3:

#   c "As I am the commanding officer and just brokered the deal, I'm going to make an executive decision."
    c "Como soy el oficial al mando y acabo de cerrar el trato, voy a tomar una decisión ejecutiva."

# game/episode016.rpy:919
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3ac6d989:

#   c "The deal stands as it is, I'm going back in ten years."
    c "El trato sigue como está, volveré dentro de diez años."

# game/episode016.rpy:920
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_51e02df5:

#   c "And I'm pretty sure we'll find a loophole somewhere to get out of this deal before the term is up."
    c "Y estoy bastante seguro de que encontraremos un resquicio en alguna parte para salirnos de este acuerdo antes de que termine el plazo."

# game/episode016.rpy:921
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_1060a349:

#   "I could see the dismay in the eyes of both Nadya and Aven, Kit looked like he was about to argue."
    "Pude ver la consternación en los ojos tanto de Nadya como de Aven, Kit parecía a punto de discutir."

# game/episode016.rpy:922
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_809df9c3:

#   "They kept silent though and allowed me to approach the Queen."
    "Sin embargo, guardaron silencio y me permitieron acercarme a la Reina."

# game/episode016.rpy:924
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4fd61473:

#   woman "Have you reached a decision?"
    woman "¿Ha tomado una decisión?"

# game/episode016.rpy:925
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_29cf02ab:

#   c "We have, your majesty."
    c "Lo hemos hecho, majestad."

# game/episode016.rpy:927
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b9559b80:

#   c "We'd like to amend the deal."
    c "Nos gustaría modificar el acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:928
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_50fd5c4d:

#   c "Nadya will return in ten years time to undergo the Tasting."
    c "Nadya volverá dentro de diez años para someterse a la Cata."

# game/episode016.rpy:930
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4ea1b34e:

#   c "The deal stands as it is."
    c "El acuerdo se mantiene tal cual."

# game/episode016.rpy:931
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5b97e80b:

#   c "I will return in ten years time to undergo another Tasting."
    c "Volveré dentro de diez años para someterme a otra cata."

# game/episode016.rpy:933
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9823fc46:

#   woman "Good."
    woman "Bien."

# game/episode016.rpy:934
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_1e3bb4fe:

#   woman "We will order everything in writing and send the documents for you to sign to your vessel."
    woman "Ordenaremos todo por escrito y le enviaremos los documentos para que los firme a su embarcación."

# game/episode016.rpy:936
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_ea68c4ec:

#   woman "Once signed, a package containing the information you desire will be forwarded."
    woman "Una vez firmado, se le enviará un paquete con la información que desee."

# game/episode016.rpy:938
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0f2b1330:

#   "With those words the audience was over and we were dismissed."
    "Con esas palabras se acabó la audiencia y nos despidieron."

# game/episode016.rpy:940
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_c26834f0:

#   "The Scolguin escorted us back to the ship, where we waited for the contract to arrive."
    "El Scolguin nos escoltó de vuelta al barco, donde esperamos a que llegara el contrato."

# game/episode016.rpy:942
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_283ea2d5:

#   "After half an hour, a Scolguin clerk approached the Bastard and presented us with a tablet containing legal documents."
    "Al cabo de media hora, un empleado de Scolguin se acercó al Bastardo y nos entregó una tableta con documentos legales."

# game/episode016.rpy:944
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a7223ff2:

#   "Nadya and I read over the document several times and she ultimately signed at the indicated spots."
    "Nadya y yo leímos el documento varias veces y al final firmó en los puntos indicados."

# game/episode016.rpy:946
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9eeade3b:

#   "I read over the document several times and ultimately signed at the indicated spots."
    "Leí el documento varias veces y finalmente firmé en los puntos indicados."

# game/episode016.rpy:948
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a8bc5d74:

#   "The clerk headed back into the bowels of the Scolguin ship, leaving us to wait on the promised data."
    "El empleado se dirigió de nuevo a las entrañas de la nave Scolguin, dejándonos a la espera de los datos prometidos."

# game/episode016.rpy:950
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_4f79394c:

#   "The Scolguin took their sweet time, but eventually a message arrived."
    "Los Scolguin se tomaron su tiempo, pero finalmente llegó un mensaje."

# game/episode016.rpy:952
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b7c7ed0b:

#   ce "The Scolguin are asking us to accept a data package."
    ce "Los Scolguin nos piden que aceptemos un paquete de datos."

# game/episode016.rpy:953
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_656322b7:

#   c "Is it legit?"
    c "¿Es legal?"

# game/episode016.rpy:954
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_fa40b707:

#   ce "Our initial scans show it’s just data."
    ce "Nuestras exploraciones iniciales muestran que son sólo datos."

# game/episode016.rpy:955
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5d10d844:

#   c "Accept the transfer and let Jade have a look at it first."
    c "Acepta la transferencia y deja que Jade le eche un vistazo primero."

# game/episode016.rpy:956
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_c15bb9f6:

#   ce "Alright."
    ce "De acuerdo."

# game/episode016.rpy:958
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bef5a625:

#   "I summoned Jade to the bridge and she got to work on one of the consoles."
    "Llamé a Jade al puente y se puso a trabajar en una de las consolas."

# game/episode016.rpy:959
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b11a50c1:

#   "Nadya joined us a while later, after hearing of the discovery."
    "Nadya se unió a nosotros un rato después, tras enterarse del descubrimiento."

# game/episode016.rpy:961
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d56cffde:

#   j "Nothing seems to be out of the ordinary."
    j "Nada parece fuera de lo normal."

# game/episode016.rpy:962
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_257fecaa:

#   j "It’s navigational data, text and some images."
    j "Son datos de navegación, texto y algunas imágenes."

# game/episode016.rpy:963
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a2fb7961:

#   c "What does it say?"
    c "¿Qué dice?"

# game/episode016.rpy:965
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a4156d12:

#   j "The Scolguin provided your father with information on a certain ancient gateway."
    j "El Scolguin proporcionó a tu padre información sobre cierta puerta antigua."

# game/episode016.rpy:966
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b30405ee:

#   j "The package contains several descriptions of the gateway by various people, presumably experiences stolen from the many sacrifices offered to the Scolguin."
    j "El paquete contiene varias descripciones del portal realizadas por diversas personas, presumiblemente experiencias robadas a los numerosos sacrificios ofrecidos al Escolguín."

# game/episode016.rpy:967
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_89aec3c1:

#   c "A gateway to where?"
    c "¿Una puerta hacia dónde?"

# game/episode016.rpy:969
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3e1d2a62:

#   j "That isn’t specified, only the location of the gate."
    j "Eso no se especifica, sólo la ubicación de la puerta."

# game/episode016.rpy:970
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_d866ffab:

#   c "So it’s a space gate?"
    c "¿Así que es una puerta espacial?"

# game/episode016.rpy:971
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_5a8c8afb:

#   j "No, it’s a planet-bound structure somewhere in the Hawwa cluster."
    j "No, es una estructura planetaria en algún lugar del cúmulo Hawwa."

# game/episode016.rpy:972
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_bd62df20:

#   c "That’s not Sovereignty-occupied space, is it?"
    c "Eso no es espacio ocupado por la soberanía, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode016.rpy:974
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_8f34c340:

#   ce "No, the Hawwa cluster is independent."
    ce "No, la agrupación de Hawwa es independiente."

# game/episode016.rpy:975
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_65ee123f:

#   ce "It’s the home of the Taagmar and not even remotely close to Sovereignty space."
    ce "Es el hogar de los Taagmar y no está ni remotamente cerca del espacio de Soberanía."

# game/episode016.rpy:976
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b4d54398:

#   c "What’s that old bastard up to?"
    c "¿Qué trama ese viejo bastardo?"

# game/episode016.rpy:978
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_538711e7:

#   na "No good, probably."
    na "Nada bueno, probablemente."

# game/episode016.rpy:979
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a540aa60:

#   na "I can’t imagine the Taagmar welcoming the Sovereignty with open arms."
    na "No me imagino a los Taagmar recibiendo al Soberano con los brazos abiertos."

# game/episode016.rpy:980
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_0f99c754:

#   c "You know of them?"
    c "¿Los conoces?"

# game/episode016.rpy:981
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_840120eb:

#   na "Yes, I’ve visited their homeworld once."
    na "Sí, he visitado su mundo una vez."

# game/episode016.rpy:982
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_68f256fa:

#   na "Their technology isn’t that advanced and they’re mostly confined to their planet."
    na "Su tecnología no es tan avanzada y están confinados en su planeta."

# game/episode016.rpy:983
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_3582703c:

#   na "It’s an old civilization though, so the existence of an old gateway doesn’t surprise me."
    na "Sin embargo, es una civilización antigua, por lo que la existencia de un antiguo portal no me sorprende."

# game/episode016.rpy:985
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_a177e106:

#   ce "Why would he seek out something like that?"
    ce "¿Por qué buscaría algo así?"

# game/episode016.rpy:986
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_23917e82:

#   na "Like the gates in space, there are several planet-bound ones, part of a separate network."
    na "Al igual que las puertas en el espacio, hay varias en los planetas, que forman parte de una red independiente."

# game/episode016.rpy:987
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_346d7fcd:

#   na "Unlike the space gates, the terrestrial portals only provide access to one specific destination."
    na "A diferencia de las puertas espaciales, los portales terrestres sólo permiten acceder a un destino concreto."

# game/episode016.rpy:988
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_b6ca9504:

#   c "So Agust has a keen interest in one specific gate that’s right in the middle of an alien civilization."
    c "Así que Agust tiene un gran interés en una puerta específica que está justo en el centro de una civilización alienígena."

# game/episode016.rpy:989
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_546fa35f:

#   c "I wonder how much of the Hawwa cluster is still intact after the Sovereignty has stomped around in it..."
    c "Me pregunto cuánto de la agrupación Hawwa sigue intacta después de que el Soberano haya pisoteado en ella..."

# game/episode016.rpy:990
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_245369f7:

#   c "I guess there’s only one way to find out."
    c "Supongo que sólo hay una forma de averiguarlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:992
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_38b0e80c:

#   ce "We’re going in, aren’t we?"
    ce "Vamos a entrar, ¿no?"

# game/episode016.rpy:993
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_fa9c380b:

#   c "Yes, that’s the plan."
    c "Sí, ese es el plan."

# game/episode016.rpy:994
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_f089f460:

#   c "But I want to know more about the situation in the Hawwa cluster first."
    c "Pero primero quiero saber más sobre la situación en la agrupación de Hawwa."

# game/episode016.rpy:995
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_562a9320:

#   c "I don’t want us to walk into a trap."
    c "No quiero que caigamos en una trampa."

# game/episode016.rpy:996
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_6959cdda:

#   c "Plot a course to a space station near the Hawwa cluster so we can put out some feelers."
    c "Traza un rumbo a una estación espacial cerca del cúmulo Hawwa para que podamos tantear el terreno."

# game/episode016.rpy:997
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_e5a13291:

#   ce "Of course."
    ce "Por supuesto."

# game/episode016.rpy:999
translate spanish ep016_scolguin_fleet_9e5cae44:

#   "Céline found us a space station that was close enough to the Hawwa cluster, but still far removed from any accidental run-ins with Sovereignty ships."
    "Céline nos encontró una estación espacial lo bastante cerca del cúmulo de Hawwa, pero aún lejos de cualquier encontronazo accidental con naves de la Soberanía."

# game/episode016.rpy:1007
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_55eaecb5:

#   "Long lines of traffic heading towards the station were the first noticeable thing we encountered when entering Altum space."
    "Las largas colas de tráfico en dirección a la estación fueron lo primero que notamos al entrar en el espacio Altum."

# game/episode016.rpy:1009
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_7d031fea:

#   c "Is this system normally as crowded?"
    c "¿Este sistema suele estar tan abarrotado?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1011
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_2ce16314:

#   ce "According to our records, it shouldn't be."
    ce "Según nuestros registros, no debería serlo."

# game/episode016.rpy:1012
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_493ce1a0:

#   ce "Altum is very much a backwater system."
    ce "Altum es un sistema muy atrasado."

# game/episode016.rpy:1013
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_f6a5e0b1:

#   c "I think you're right, because those lines don't seem to be moving much, so they must have trouble processing all the incoming traffic."
    c "Creo que tienes razón, porque esas líneas no parecen moverse mucho, así que deben tener problemas para procesar todo el tráfico entrante."

# game/episode016.rpy:1014
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_fea20c8e:

#   c "Well, let's wait in line and see what's up."
    c "Bueno, esperemos en la cola a ver qué pasa."

# game/episode016.rpy:1016
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_8a5dbfe2:

#   "The traffic moved at a glacial pace and the chatter on the comms was filled with disgruntled trading vessels demanding to skip the queue."
    "El tráfico avanzaba a un ritmo glacial y las conversaciones por los comunicadores se llenaban de naves comerciales descontentas que exigían saltarse la cola."

# game/episode016.rpy:1017
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_d3fde45e:

#   "Several hours later, we were in range to request docking permission."
    "Varias horas más tarde, estábamos al alcance para solicitar permiso de atraque."

# game/episode016.rpy:1020
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_4cd34f96:

#   man "Please state the nature of your visit."
    man "Indique la naturaleza de su visita."

# game/episode016.rpy:1021
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_64b80a6a:

#   c "Resupply and R&R."
    c "Reabastecimiento y R&R."

# game/episode016.rpy:1022
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_a7cb0f04:

#   man "Acknowledged."
    man "Reconocido."

# game/episode016.rpy:1023
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_5eaf061c:

#   man "Be aware though that supplies are constrained at the moment as our docking bays are nearly at full capacity."
    man "Tenga en cuenta, sin embargo, que los suministros son limitados en este momento, ya que nuestras bahías de atraque están casi a plena capacidad."

# game/episode016.rpy:1024
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_a67df695:

#   man "Your vessel is cleared to dock."
    man "Su buque está autorizado a atracar."

# game/episode016.rpy:1026
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_5e847f30:

#   "After exchanging the necessary information, Céline initiated the docking sequence."
    "Tras intercambiar la información necesaria, Céline inició la secuencia de acoplamiento."

# game/episode016.rpy:1027
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_7153b23b:

#   "The officer hadn't exaggerated, nearly all of the docking bays for larger vessels were already occupied."
    "El oficial no había exagerado, casi todos los muelles de atraque para buques más grandes estaban ya ocupados."

# game/episode016.rpy:1029
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_c86b8656:

#   "The Bastard fit into one of the smaller bays, which were already teeming with activity."
    "El Bastardo cabía en una de las bahías más pequeñas, que ya rebosaban de actividad."

# game/episode016.rpy:1031
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_7d648703:

#   "As we disembarked and got a closer look at the people crowding the docks, it became clear that this logjam was very much out of the ordinary."
    "Al desembarcar y observar más de cerca a la gente que se agolpaba en los muelles, quedó claro que aquel atasco era algo fuera de lo común."

# game/episode016.rpy:1032
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_3fda892a:

#   "Large groups of people shuffled aimlessly around at the docks looking haunted and destitute."
    "Grandes grupos de personas deambulaban sin rumbo por los muelles con aspecto atormentado y desamparado."

# game/episode016.rpy:1033
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_b6dfbdec:

#   "A member of the station's docking crew took note of our puzzlement."
    "Un miembro de la tripulación de atraque de la estación tomó nota de nuestra perplejidad."

# game/episode016.rpy:1036
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_72864570:

#   man "Didn't hear about the refugees, did you?"
    man "No te enteraste de lo de los refugiados, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1037
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_dc63075f:

#   c "No, I can't say that we have."
    c "No, no puedo decir que lo hayamos hecho."

# game/episode016.rpy:1038
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_9860bac1:

#   c "The amount of traffic outside surprised us, but this is something else."
    c "La cantidad de tráfico fuera nos sorprendió, pero esto es otra cosa."

# game/episode016.rpy:1039
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_119180bd:

#   c "Where are the refugees from?"
    c "¿De dónde son los refugiados?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_d4ea3fa1:

#   man "All from a specific system in the Hawwa cluster."
    man "Todo desde un sistema específico del clúster Hawwa."

# game/episode016.rpy:1053
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_b6cfd3bb:

#   man "Those Sovereignty fucks invaded the habitable systems a while ago, started shooting up everything."
    man "Esos cabrones de Soberanía invadieron los sistemas habitables hace un tiempo, empezaron a disparar a todo."

# game/episode016.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_f7ac48f8:

#   c "How bad is it?"
    c "¿Es muy grave?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1055
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_c31096b7:

#   man "Very, the entire cluster is a warzone."
    man "Muy, todo el clúster es una zona de guerra."

# game/episode016.rpy:1056
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_dab9d858:

#   c "And nobody has come to help the cluster fight back?"
    c "¿Y nadie ha venido a ayudar a la agrupación a defenderse?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_4b3dddda:

#   man "No one."
    man "A nadie."

# game/episode016.rpy:1058
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_e717a883:

#   man "The cluster is pretty empty and the people that do live in it don't trade much with others."
    man "La agrupación está bastante vacía y la gente que vive en ella no comercia mucho con los demás."

# game/episode016.rpy:1059
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_e3f7a303:

#   man "Nothing much of value over there anyway."
    man "De todas formas, allí no hay nada de mucho valor."

# game/episode016.rpy:1060
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_7f4fe43a:

#   c "You're saying the Taagmar don't have many friends?"
    c "¿Dices que los Taagmar no tienen muchos amigos?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1061
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_b601c9ae:

#   man "Exactly."
    man "Exactamente."

# game/episode016.rpy:1062
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_58c4793f:

#   man "And nobody wants to offend the Sovereignty, because who knows what they'll do to you in retaliation."
    man "Y nadie quiere ofender a la Soberanía, porque quién sabe lo que te harán en represalia."

# game/episode016.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_d13a1432:

#   c "Nothing positive, I'd wager."
    c "Nada positivo, apostaría."

# game/episode016.rpy:1065
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_78d2be91:

#   man "So we help by taking in refugees, but other than that it's safe to say the Hawwa cluster is already lost."
    man "Así que ayudamos acogiendo refugiados, pero aparte de eso es seguro decir que la agrupación de Hawwa ya está perdida."

# game/episode016.rpy:1066
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_17bbf90f:

#   c "I wonder why the Sovereignty is doing all this."
    c "Me pregunto por qué la Soberanía está haciendo todo esto."

# game/episode016.rpy:1067
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_ecb32491:

#   c "The Hawwa cluster isn't neighboring any of Sovereignty space, so it's not a question of expansion."
    c "El cúmulo de Hawwa no es vecino de ningún espacio de Soberanía, así que no es una cuestión de expansión."

# game/episode016.rpy:1069
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_27f92de5:

#   man "Who knows why those genocidal maniacs do what they do..."
    man "Quién sabe por qué esos maníacos genocidas hacen lo que hacen..."

# game/episode016.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_7db56046:

#   "The dock worker had lost interest by then and turned away to resume the work he'd been doing."
    "Para entonces, el trabajador del muelle había perdido el interés y se dio la vuelta para reanudar el trabajo que había estado haciendo."

# game/episode016.rpy:1072
translate spanish ep016_altum_approach_ce770a68:

#   "We made our way further into the station, determined to find out more about Agust's latest misadventures."
    "Nos adentramos en la estación, decididos a averiguar más sobre las últimas desventuras de Agust."

# game/episode016.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_d1197370:

#   "Someone was waiting inside the guest quarters as I returned from a trip to the city center."
    "Alguien esperaba dentro de la habitación de invitados cuando volví de un viaje al centro de la ciudad."

# game/episode016.rpy:1080
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_3039d05f:

#   "It turned out to be Lilly."
    "Resultó ser Lilly."

# game/episode016.rpy:1082
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_e0fe3f99:

#   "After half an hour I received a message from Lilly."
    "Al cabo de media hora recibí un mensaje de Lilly."

# game/episode016.rpy:1083
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_d32d73be:

#   "She was apparently waiting for me in the guest quarters where we met with Nkoy Arlya before."
    "Al parecer, me esperaba en la habitación de invitados donde antes nos reunimos con Nkoy Arlya."

# game/episode016.rpy:1085
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_e012cb0f:

#   l "We had some unfinished business and I felt that the Bastard was a little too crowded."
    l "Teníamos asuntos pendientes y me pareció que el Bastard estaba demasiado lleno."

# game/episode016.rpy:1087
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_152907ad:

#   l "But now I’m not sure."
    l "Pero ahora no estoy seguro."

# game/episode016.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_73c2fcc2:

#   c "Why not?"
    c "¿Por qué no?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1089
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_52e7718e:

#   l "Because of all the windows."
    l "Por todas las ventanas."

# game/episode016.rpy:1090
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_bc607f85:

#   c "Oh, I believe I can do something about that."
    c "Creo que puedo hacer algo al respecto."

# game/episode016.rpy:1091
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_7aab2a4e:

#   "I uttered a command and all the windows went opaque."
    "Pronuncié una orden y todas las ventanas se volvieron opacas."

# game/episode016.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep016_uailea_lilly_9e4ee60e:

#   l "Yes, that’s much better!"
    l "¡Sí, mucho mejor!"

# game/episode016.rpy:1102
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_4514cfba:

#   "Nadya had left me a note in my quarters earlier, asking me to come to a location in the city."
    "Nadya me había dejado antes una nota en mis aposentos, pidiéndome que fuera a un lugar de la ciudad."

# game/episode016.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_1a7dca09:

#   "The place turned out to be a communal bath."
    "El lugar resultó ser un baño comunal."

# game/episode016.rpy:1105
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_7075fa20:

#   "I passed several half-naked Rhenkoy and wondered why Nadya had chosen this spot."
    "Pasé junto a varios Rhenkoy semidesnudos y me pregunté por qué Nadya había elegido este lugar."

# game/episode016.rpy:1106
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_efac13fa:

#   "One of the Rhenkoy approached me."
    "Uno de los Rhenkoy se me acercó."

# game/episode016.rpy:1109
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_d7eea082:

#   woman "Are you [p_name]?"
    woman "¿Eres [p_name]?"

# game/episode016.rpy:1110
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_b63d6bf3:

#   c "I am."
    c "Lo soy."

# game/episode016.rpy:1111
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_bd2faa4d:

#   woman "Your friend is waiting for you."
    woman "Tu amigo te está esperando."

# game/episode016.rpy:1112
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_9559169b:

#   woman "Follow me."
    woman "Sígueme."

# game/episode016.rpy:1114
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_cd0b2f20:

#   "I trailed the Rhenkoy woman who guided me further into the building."
    "Seguí a la mujer Rhenkoy, que me guió hacia el interior del edificio."

# game/episode016.rpy:1115
translate spanish ep016_uailea_nadya_ace07406:

#   woman "Your friend is waiting behind that gate."
